PrecisRegulations Amending the MIGRATORY BIRDS REGULATIONS which establish special hunting seasons in selected areas of Quebec and Manitoba in order to reduce the Greater and the Lesser Snow Goose population, authorize the use of special methods and equipment during the hunt and allow for an increase in the harvest of Ross Geese as a result.

precis:
Regulations Amending the MIGRATORY BIRDS REGULATIONS which establish
special hunting seasons in selected areas of Quebec and Manitoba in order
to reduce the Greater and the Lesser Snow Goose population, authorize the
use of special methods and equipment during the hunt and allow for an
increase in the harvest of Ross Geese as a result.
